<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA24">
<l>varuṅkā lirunilaṉu mālvicumpuṅ kāṟṟu</l>
<l>neruṅkutī nīruruvu māṉāṉ – poruntuñ</l>
<l>cuṭarāḻi yoṉṟuṭaiyāṉ cūḻkaḻalē nāḷun</l>
<l>toṭarāḻi neñcē toḻutu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, at the time he came, was vast land and dark sky, wind</l>
<l>and the form of approaching fire [and] water, the one who possesses</l>
<l>a singular befitting glowing discus, to the anklet that encirles his [feet]</l>
<l>link yourself daily, immerse yourself, heart, in worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
